why we've got to do this...

160
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:38,555
what happened
with the first Sil.

161
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:42,072
And why you have to be prepared.

162
00:14:42,280 --> 00:14:44,350
Survival of the fittest.
