173
00:15:28,280 --> 00:15:30,350
<i>in the crew recovery vehicle</i>
<i>are en route.</i>

174
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:33,634
Thanks, Houston.
It's good to be home.

175
00:15:41,640 --> 00:15:43,153
- Thanks.
