184
00:16:34,560 --> 00:16:37,154
<i>Back when President Kennedy</i>
<i>began the space program...</i>

185
00:16:37,600 --> 00:16:39,989
I was just a very young
assistant up on the Hill.

186
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:43,112
It didn't take me long to realize
that he was a visionary...

187
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:45,158
and that I shared that vision.

188
00:16:45,720 --> 00:16:47,392
Later on,
when I became a senator...

189
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:51,275
I was determined to push our program
even further into space.

190
00:16:51,880 --> 00:16:54,952
And so today,
Jack Kennedy's vision...

191
00:16:55,160 --> 00:16:58,869
