on behalf of my wonderful crew...

210
00:18:47,280 --> 00:18:50,113
to represent
the mission to Mars...

211
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,512
and an image
that comes to my mind...

212
00:18:53,360 --> 00:18:55,874
is looking through the porthole...

213
00:18:57,200 --> 00:18:58,713
at the blue-white globe...

214
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:00,795
beautiful...

215
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:04,072
so fragile, so small.

216
00:19:06,760 --> 00:19:08,352
And I thought to myself...

217
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:12,555
